<h1>What's an Attribute?</h1>
<p>That's when you add something inside the tag, like:</p>
<p>&lt;p class=&quot;myClass&quot;&gt;</p>
<p>Class is the attribute.</p>
<p>They don't always have to be equal to something, for example:</p>
<p>&lt;input name=&quot;myName&quot; disabled&gt;</p>
<p>Just the mere presence of the disabled attribute means it's disabled.</p>
